<H1>Creating a distribution list</H1>

<P>A distribution list is very useful where a group of users
need to communicate amongst themselves on a regular
basis.</P>

<P>Each list is given a name just like any other user.  By
addressing a message to the list name, the sender can be
sure that everyone will receive a copy.</P>

<P>You cannot set up a distribution list yourself. Ask your
<A HREF="../local/sysadm.html">system administrator</A> to set one up for you.</P>

